Usage: attachModulePort [-help] <moduleName> <portName> <netName> [-noNewPort]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<moduleName>            # Name of module (string, required)
<portName>              # Name of the port (string, required)
<netName>               # Name of the net (string, required)
-noNewPort              # No new port is allowed to be created regardless
                        # whether the given module port and net are in the same
                        # hierarchy or not (bool, optional)